Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hey, Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:08.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm so glad someone's here. Could you zip me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Sure.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:15.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Can you believe no one between my apartment and here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...offered to do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}People.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:23.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So why are you so dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mike's picking me up for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:28.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}How's that going? Is it getting serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:32.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know. I don't know. I mean, I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:35.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But am I ready to take my Grade A loins off the meat market?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm not quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know, I really admire your whole dating attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's so healthy. I'm always like, "Is this moving too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Is this moving too slow? Where's this going? "
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know. You are a bit of a drama queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:57.74,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're so much better off. You just go from guy to guy having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:02.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...and not worrying that it never turns into anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wouldn't say "never."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:07.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know, there is that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay, well, what about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay, there's gotta be someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:17.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- There isn't! That's what I'm saying.  - Oh, my God, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:21.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know. And yet, here you are, all ready for the next date.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:25.97,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I can't believe I never realized this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:30.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm in my 30s, and I've never been in a long-term relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Oh, my God, what's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:39.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There's nothing wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:44.59,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I mean, you don't strike me as the type of person that wants to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, please... Please don't cry because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:54.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know what I'm talking about, okay? I've been divorced three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.59,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}At least you've been married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Oh, my God! I want to trade lives with Ross? !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Phoebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:08.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- What's wrong?  - Nothing. I'm excited about our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:14.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mike, this is Ross Geller. Ross, this is Mike...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Sorry, I didn't catch that.  - Mike Hanigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Ross Geller.  - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So are you sure you're ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Do you have a compact in your purse?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Hey, Joey.  - This girl won't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I can't tell if she's hot or not. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Joey, I am not going to objectify women with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But if her face is as nice as her ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Mama!  - All right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Have you talked to Chandler?  - He has to stay in Tulsa this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- How come?  - I don't know. He has to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:41.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There's some big rush on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:49.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Damn it. I'm gonna have to start listening when he talks about his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you fly out there and surprise him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Maybe I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:59.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We'll have a little second honeymoon at the Tulsa Ramada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:05.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You should bring your black see-through teddy with the attached garters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- How do you know I have one of those?  - Didrt until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hot. Not hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I said that I think you're hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And... now I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I thought you said "hi."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That would've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:40.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll try that. Hi, I'm Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm Hayley.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:47.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Look, I don't normally ask out women that I meet in coffeehouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gesundheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I would love to go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.51,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Really? Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Did I...? Did I actually ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's just where you were going. I figured I'd help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:15.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You don't seem like the kind of guy who does this a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- So how'd the date go?  - Well, it was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Every time I thought about what you said, I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- So he hasn't called?  - Would you call this girl:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"Thanks for... a lovely... evening"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Now I feel terrible. This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know what you should feel terrible about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This could have been my serious guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He was sweet and smart and funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.71,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know how hard it is to meet a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We are a rare breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What a great dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:07.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thanks again for letting me have that last piece of cake at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:11.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're welcome again. I'm gonna go make some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Can I get you anything?  - Do you have any cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So this is going pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Dinner was nice. We've got a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Victoria's Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We even like the same books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There's a scary painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:41.21,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I think I've been scared by that painting before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know what? This whole place looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have definitely been in this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know I've seen this weird plant before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It did that the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Oh, my God. I've gone out with this girl before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah! We had sex on this couch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.43,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And then on that chair, and... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, we didn't do it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:08.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...which is weird, because it seems like a perfectly good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.69,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hey, Mike. Sorry to just drop by like this. Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:24.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm Ross. Phoebe's friend from the coffeehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:34.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I really, really need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:40.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're not gonna try and get me to join a cult, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, it's just, you know, you have that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Damn Supercuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.52,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Well, what's up? Is Phoebe okay?  - Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Phoebe is great. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm an idiot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.12,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Right before you guys went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...I accidentally got her all upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's why she was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yes. Yeah, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:13.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, I said something stupid about her never having had a serious relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:16.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But you should know, she is so much fun. A wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:20.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Please, don't blow her off.  - I'm not gonna blow her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I just spoke to her. We're going out tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:28.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I mean, I hope that's okay with you, stranger from the coffeehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Well, then, I didn't need to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You or the four other Mike Hanigans I bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:43.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Wait. Wait. Wait. Wait. Is that true what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.76,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Phoebe's never had a serious relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Of course she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If she's never had a serious relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...do you think I'd go around broadcasting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:58.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...like some kind of unstoppable moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- But you did say it.  - Yes. Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:07.61,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I will also say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:10.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...what I'm about to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...vis-? vis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...the following.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:22.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Phoebe has never had a serious relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...since...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:29.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...her super-serious relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.40,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...Vikram.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:36.67,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Vikram?  - What? That's a real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.55,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why couldn't they have sent me to Texas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.58,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.99,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Maybe I'll hit the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Who am I kidding? Pay-per-view porn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Do not disturb! Do not disturb!  - Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.72,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Monica?  - Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.83,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, everything's great. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...watching some regular television there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What a pleasant surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- I'm gonna go freshen up, okay?  - Okay, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Hello.  - Hey, Rach, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay, I just got to Chandler's room, and I caught him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...molesting himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That couldn't have been pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But you know, guys do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Well, the weird part is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:16.45,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...he was getting off... to a shark-attack show!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:21.54,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- No!  - Yes! Chandler watches shark porn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- While watching sharks?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are you sure that's what he was doing?
