Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:59.07,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yes. Just some good, old-fashioned, American, girl-on-girl action.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:04.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Can I tell you how happy that makes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You are an amazing wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:12.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Really, you are amazing. You were actually gonna do this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:16.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where do you find the strength and the understanding for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:20.79,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm very, very drunk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:30.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Ordinarily, I would talk to her, but my confidence is shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Did I sleep with her? Did I not sleep with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:39.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Maybe this is a wake-up call. You know, about your whole dating attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:44.48,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're in your 30s and you have never been in a long-term relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:46.75,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Here you go from woman to woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}...meaningless experience to meaningless experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:53.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Never even worrying that it doesn't turn into something more serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:56.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're right. I love my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:03.24,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I actually did sleep with her.
